# 📉 Telco Customer Churn Prediction

This project explores customer churn using a real-world telecom dataset.

## 🔍 Objective
Build predictive models to identify customers likely to churn and uncover key churn drivers.

## 📊 Tools & Methods
- Python, Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn
- Logistic Regression, XGBoost
- SHAP for explainability
- Google Colab

## 📈 Key Insights
- Month-to-month contracts and high charges were strong churn indicators
- XGBoost outperformed logistic regression in accuracy and recall

## 📁 Files
- `telco_churn_prediction.ipynb` – Full code and analysis
- `README.md` – Project overview

## ✅ Result
This project demonstrates strong skills in data cleaning, modeling, and turning insights into action.
